beacon-depositor.Description: An address that has deposited ETH into the Beacon Chain to become a validator.

lido.Description: Lido is a liquid staking solution for ETH 2.0 backed by industry-leading staking providers. Lido lets users stake their ETH - without locking assets or maintaining infrastructure - whilst participating in on-chain activities.

staking.Description: The process of holding funds in a cryptocurrency wallet to support the operations of a network.
